Package eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.wrappers.single.auxiliaries

Class ParameterValueResponseWrapper

java.lang.Object
eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.wrappers.ResponseWrapper
eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.wrappers.single.auxiliaries.ParameterValueResponseWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ParameterValueResponseWrapper extends ResponseWrapper implements Serializable
This class wraps the responses travelling from the persistence layer back to the API for a more complete reporting of problems / unsuccessful requests on Parameter Values. Used for Single Objects (as opposed to a Collection).
Since:
version 0.4.0
Author:
Angela-Maria Despotopoulou [Athens, Greece]
